[Mon 2026-04-20 02:26 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/2). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.

[Subagent Task]: Implement a complete new admin dashboard UI for the AHV DTLX Driving Training system. The design is for "PHÚC AN" brand.

## Tech Stack
- React 18 + Vite
- Ant Design 5
- Recharts
- React Icons
- Bootstrap CSS (existing)

## Workspace
- Frontend: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend/`
- Current branch: `feat/cms-driving-training-design`
- Existing dashboard: `src/pages/dashboard/`

## Design Spec — PHÚC AN Dashboard

### Color Palette
- Background: white + light gray (#F5F6F8)
- Primary accent: Blue (#3B82F6)
- KPI positive: Green (#10B981)
- KPI negative: Red (#EF4444)
- Chart colors: Pink (#EC4899), Green (#10B981), Orange (#F59E0B), Yellow (#FBBF24), Purple (#8B5CF6), Blue (#3B82F6)

### Layout Structure
```
[Main Content area - full page width]
[Header: page title "Dasboard" | Filters: Location (Hà Nội), Time (T6-T8/2026), Export button | search + notifications + profile]
[KPI Cards Row: 4 cards - Doanh thu, Chi phí, Lợi nhuận, Công nợ]
[Growth Area Chart - full width, Jan-Jun]
[Row: Cost Donut+List (left 50%) | Course List (right 50%)]
[Student & Teacher Line Chart - full width, 12 months]
```

### Components to Create

#### 1. `src/pages/dashboard/components/DashboardHeader.jsx`
- Page title: "Dasboard" (with the typo per user spec!)
- Below title: filters row - Location select "Hà Nội", Time select "T6-T8/2026", Export button
- Right side: search input (placeholder "Tìm kiếm..."), notification bell icon, admin profile circle with "A"
- White bg, clean layout
- Use Ant Design: Select, Input.Search, Badge, Avatar

#### 2. `src/pages/dashboard/components/KPICards.jsx`
- 4 cards in a row (col-3 each on desktop, col-6 on tablet, col-12 on mobile)
- Each card: white bg, rounded 12px, soft shadow, padding 20px
- Card content:
  - Top: colored icon circle (bg colored circle with white icon)
  - Label (gray, small): "Doanh thu" / "Chi phí" / "Lợi nhuận" / "Công nợ"
  - Value (large, bold): "2.000.000 ₫"
  - Badge (top-right): "+42%" green / "-20%" red / "+22%" green / "-11%" red
- Card 1 - Doanh thu: icon bg green (#10B981), arrow-up icon
- Card 2 - Chi phí: icon bg red (#EF4444), arrow-down icon  
- Card 3 - Lợi nhuận: icon bg blue (#3B82F6), chart icon
- Card 4 - Công nợ: icon bg orange (#F59E0B), credit-card icon
- Use react-icons for icons
- Hover: translateY(-2px) and stronger shadow

#### 3. `src/pages/dashboard/components/GrowthChart.jsx`
- Recharts AreaChart, full width in a white card
- Title "Tăng trưởng" top-left inside card
- Data (dummy): Jan: 30, Feb: 45, Mar: 40, Apr: 60, May: 55, Jun: 80
- Area fill: green (#10B981) with gradient from opacity 0.3 to 0
- X-axis: month names, Y-axis: numeric
- Smooth curve (type="monotone")
- No right-side legend
- Height: ~300px

#### 4. `src/pages/dashboard/components/CostDonutChart.jsx`
- White card container, title "Chi phí" top-left
- Left side: Recharts PieChart (donut/pie), ~180px diameter
  - 6 segments with equal values (20% each): Sửa chữa xe, Thay lốp xe, Gửi xe, Thay dầu, Rửa kính, Văn phòng
  - Colors: Pink (#EC4899), Green (#10B981), Orange (#F59E0B), Yellow (#FBBF24), Purple (#8B5CF6), Blue (#3B82F6)
  - Center label: "Tổng" on top, "2.000.000 ₫" below
- Right side: list with 6 rows
  - Each row: colored dot + name + percentage badge + thin gray progress bar (all at ~70% filled to show visual)
  - Row color matches pie segment
- Responsive: stack vertically on mobile

#### 5. `src/pages/dashboard/components/CourseList.jsx`
- White card, title "Khóa học" top-left
- Table header: Mã khóa | Học viên | Biến động
- Rows (all dummy):
  - KH2026 | 73 | +41 (green badge)
  - C1k12 | 73 | +1 (green badge)
  - LX1010 | 73 | +4 (green badge)
  - B2auto | 65 | -3 (red badge)
  - A1 | 58 | +12 (green badge)
- Clean table styling: no full borders, just bottom borders on rows
- Badge colors: green for positive, red for negative

#### 6. `src/pages/dashboard/components/StudentTeacherChart.jsx`
- White card, title "Học viên & Giáo viên" top-left
- Recharts LineChart, full width
- X-axis: 12 months T1-T12/2026
- Two lines:
  - Học viên: green (#10B981), circle dot markers, smooth curve
  - Giáo viên: orange (#F59E0B), circle dot markers, smooth curve
- Tooltip: shows month + count for both
- Height: ~280px
- Simple legend at top or bottom

### Replace `src/pages/dashboard/chart/index.jsx`
New content:
```jsx
