## Important Rules
1. Write COMPLETE, WORKING code - no TODOs, no placeholders
2. Use real Recharts charts - AreaChart, PieChart, LineChart, Tooltip, Legend, ResponsiveContainer
3. All data is DUMMY - hardcoded arrays
4. Import icons from 'react-icons/ai' or 'react-icons/hi' (Ant Design icons / Heroicons)
5. Use Ant Design: Select, Input, Badge, Avatar, Card
6. Responsive: use Bootstrap grid (row, col-12, col-xl-6, col-3, etc.)
7. Follow existing code style: import React from 'react', default export

